node.text: Throwback to 2019 when it was a rainy day in Minnesota! My buddy Jeff Walker races at the professional level of motocross and his dad “Pauly D” is a pilot and also a friend and Jeff’s mechanic. Look forward to cheering Jeff on this upcoming season! Check out Jeff’s YouTube channel! @jeffwalker84

node.text: With nicknames like “The Pilot Maker” and “The Washing Machine” ..flying the T6 is a blast! New video dropping on YouTube this week. node.text: One of my favorite destinations in the French Alps! I have been flying around on flight sim exploring this beautiful area. Definitely some tricky airports to test your skills! @boseaviation @pivotcase #steveo1kinevo #flightsimulator

node.text: Have you ever wondered what happens when a stray bullet hits your airplane? On my YouTube channel this week I will show you the painful process and the cost to fix it! @boseaviation  @pivotcase  #steveo1kinevo

node.text: Throwback to 2019 when it was a rainy day in Minnesota! My buddy Jeff Walker races at the professional level of motocross and his dad “Pauly D” is a pilot and also a friend and Jeff’s mechanic. Look forward to cheering Jeff on this upcoming season! Check out Jeff’s YouTube channel! @jeffwalker84

node.text: Nothing better than being tugged out of the event to the departure line, watching the final moments of the airshow, and getting ready to blast off into the sky to go home! @boseaviation @pivotcase #steveo1kinevo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by steveo1kinevo on May 12, 2021. May be an image of airplane and sky.

node.text: After Bullet Holes and many years of Engine Oil Issues can we PLEASE get this airplane working correctly! I can’t wait to get this airplane fixed so I can get back to work! @dahertbm @prattandwhitneyca we need to get this airplane back up in the sky! Let’s get this right and make sure it gets fixed properly! Companies that do it properly.. @boseaviation @pivotcase and of course myself.. #steveo1kinevo
